metatags.og:description:
Founder at Tilt Intimates | Tilting the Status Quo. · Hey there! I'm the co-founder who heads all things brand at Tilt. We're making comfort sexy in a category that often innovates for the male gaze instead of function. 

Before the Tilting of Status Quo - I graduated from the University of East Anglia, United Kingdom, on the Dean's scholarship with a major in International relations and a minor in Media. As a side-effect of growing up lovestruck with artistic works, I am ever keen to use words and visual storytelling that break through the clutter and stir the final consumer. 

Over the last eight years, I've worked for large and small brands to discover the unifying truth behind eye-catching media: it's simple, really. Good inventions with an authentic plot make for a truly great brand. · Experience: Tilt · Education: University of East Anglia · Location: Mumbai · 500+ connections on LinkedIn.
